00:27:38.878 --> 00:27:39.628
Ciao.

309
00:27:40.132 --> 00:27:42.096
- Oh, ciao.
- Ehi! Timothy.


310
00:27:42.216 --> 00:27:42.916
Ehi.

311
00:27:43.446 --> 00:27:45.046
