la palla, Timothy.


343
00:28:59.794 --> 00:29:01.994
<i>Forza! Muoviti, muoviti!</i>

344
00:29:02.499 --> 00:29:04.309
- In prigione.
- Devi spiegarglielo,


345
00:29:04.429 --> 00:29:06.394
- Non sta capendo.
- Timothy!


346
00:29:06.514 --> 00:29:08.269
Timothy. Timothy. Timothy.

347
00:29:08.389 --> 00:29:12.016
- Mancano solo 5 bambini.
