454
00:35:06.031 --> 00:35:06.931
Timothy!

455
00:35:08.423 --> 00:35:09.073
No!

456
00:35:09.608 --> 00:35:11.284
Ehi... chi e' stato?

457
00:35:11.573 --> 00:35:13.223
