989
01:10:43.118 --> 01:10:44.170
Ehm, Timothy?

990
01:10:44.290 --> 01:10:45.664
- Ehi, piccolo.
- Ehi.


991
01:10:45.784 --> 01:10:46.984
Va tutto bene.

