01:19:27.726 --> 01:19:28.676
<i>Si'! Si'!</i>

1118
01:19:29.144 --> 01:19:30.859
<i>Eccola, eccola!</i>

1119
01:19:30.979 --> 01:19:32.629
<i>Colpiscila, colpiscila!</i>

1120
01:19:33.687 --> 01:19:36.137
